l:dependency.name: S3 package parameter plugin
l:dependency.l:description: A rather specific use-case. A Jenkins plugin that will look up a AWS S3 hosted Yum or Apt repo's database, and glean any information needed to populate a Jenkins parameter dropdown. The primary driver for me to develop this was the ability to look up the packages in the repo in order to call MCollective with a package that we know exists.
